        emp-project-management-service]
        style ProjectSvc fill:#4d004d,stroke:#c299c2
        FinancialSvc[REPO-SVC-FINANCIAL
        emp-financial-service]
        style FinancialSvc fill:#4d004d,stroke:#c299c2
        UserSvc[REPO-SVC-USER
