	g.sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant WebApp as emp-frontend-webapp
    participant APIGW as emp-api-gateway
    participant S3 as AWS S3
    participant MsgBus as Message Bus (RabbitMQ)
    participant AIWorker as emp-ai-processing-worker
    participant DB as Project Mgmt DB

    User->>WebApp: Uploads SOW file
    WebApp->>APIGW: POST /api/v1/sow/upload (file)
    activate APIGW
    APIGW->>S3: Store original document
    APIGW->>MsgBus: Publish [SowUploadedEvent]
    APIGW-->>WebApp: 202 Accepted (sow_id)
    deactivate APIGW

    activate AIWorker
    MsgBus->>AIWorker: Deliver [SowUploadedEvent]
    AIWorker->>S3: Fetch SOW document
    AIWorker->>AIWorker: Process SOW (PII, Extract, Embed)
    AIWorker->>DB: Update ProjectBrief & SOW Status
    AIWorker-->>MsgBus: ACK Message
    deactivate AIWorker